Class GeographicCoordinate

  • java.lang.Object
    • pythagoras.d.Vector3

        • com.atc.simulator.vectors.GeographicCoordinate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IVector3

    public class GeographicCoordinate
extends SphericalCoordinate
    Represents a geographic position using latitude, longitude, altitude (above mean sea level) See https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geographic_coordinate_system
    See Also:
